value.name: T-Birds' Schmitz named women's regional Coach of the Year
value.description: NEW ORLEANS, La. - Cloud County Community College head women's track and field coach Ted Schmitz has been named the United States Track and Field Cross Country Coaches Association Outdoor Track and Field Central Region Women's Coach of the Year as announced by the USTFCCCA on Wednesday.
